<p class="posted"><strong>Posted by <a target="_blank" title="http://claws.guildportal.com" href="http://mobhunter.com/mt/mobhunter_post21.cgi?__mode=red;id=356">Talaen</a> at October 11, 2004 04:40 PM</strong></p>
